nodes.text: Docking Bay 5 was a docking bay at the spaceport in Black Spire Outpost on the planet Batuu. During the First Order occupation of the planet, Docking Bay 5 hosted Ohnaka Transport Solutions, where the pirate-turned-legitimate Hondo Ohnaka hired flight crews to pilot the Millennium Falcon on runs to Corellia.

Docking Bay 5 first appeared as the setting for the theme park attraction Millennium Falcon: Smuggler's Run, which opened along with the rest of the themed land, Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge on May 31, 2019 at Disneyland Park.
